Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:40.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in bed, Scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:46.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You must still have a fever,\Nafter that beating you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:47.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier left you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Says it's money to get your glasses fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.85,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's his farewell gift to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.97,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you apologize to Turtle for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.53,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I said terrible things to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.88,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Turtle said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:33.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna stay your friend forever,\Nso don't you dare come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be friends no\Nmatter where we are, Scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:44.90,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:53.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, guys...\NI have to run away with Eri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:58.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even run to the ends\Nof the earth if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off to work now, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:19.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you helping\NMaeda with work today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.51,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.15,RAINBOW31,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go and get you checked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:08.87,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ryu.\NDo you know where Senso Temple is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:15.43,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tree there that\Nwas burned in the war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,and only it's base escaped the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet there at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:28.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come, so wait for me, Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm way too early...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.39,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.59,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri! You're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Eri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.43,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eri?\N--She isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. She was just here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.51,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she..!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting is part of the fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I read somewhere\Nthat girls are always late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.51,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late..!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure no one noticed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:08.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:28.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.33,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I said such terrible things to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:44.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Turtle...\NI think of you as a friend, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:51.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be self-centered and\Nshameless of me, but I really do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.47,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:01.20,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you didn't really sleep with Eri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to beat sense into\Nme out of honest concern for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.78,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri's the one for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:24.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She and I are going to be happy together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to become\Na responsible grownup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:42.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet at 2:00 next Tuesday,\Ninside Senso Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.04,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think... something\Nmight've happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:42.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Turtle...\NYou knew this would happen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.21,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew this would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Scam... Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Laugh at me, Turtle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be helped that\Nmy plan backfired on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's pathetic, but this is just who I am."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:25.57,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pouring rain drenched\NScam's heart as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.36,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mario! It's me! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:45.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So she never came?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy waited for hours in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'd get a fever doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:00.12,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a real shock, though.\NThrowing his life away like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:05.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He really put\Neverything on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:19.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Scam was better\Nnow that his fever's passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.88,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,but he still hasn't said a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:28.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get to work.\NCould you watch him for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:36.83,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Scam! Rikidosan is gonna\Nbe wrestling on TV tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.19,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch on the TVs in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go shopping for dinner, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make stew tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a really good recipe at the dojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:16.19,RAINBOW31,,0000,0000,0000,,University Student\Nand Prostitute Commit Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Scam! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The vegetables were cheap,\Nso I bought a lot--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:26.84,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.70,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go? To the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.20,RAINBOW31,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Crane
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to seeing you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.25,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you read the papers?\NEri's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.47,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:58.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know! Damn selfish\Nof her too; she still owed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.45,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to her younger sister, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:02.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:08.06,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,She was working so hard\Nto put her sister through school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:16.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It sounds like that woman\Nhad you completely fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That broad didn't have a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.72,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, there was one family member...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Her drug addict of a mother who\Nsold Eri to me and ran off with a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:42.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just forget\Nabout her and get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:47.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have some fun\Nwhile you're here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a nice girl for you!\NI'll make it cheap, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.53,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with you, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:01.96,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you know?!\NAll you can think about is money..!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:06.86,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now! You're the one\Nwho paid money to buy Eri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:13.48,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I didn't get to know Eri either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:21.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know a thing about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:27.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to admit it,\Nbut I'm no different from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a piece of shit, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I don't resent the fact that\Nshe didn't open up to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't feel sad because I\Nassumed we had loved each other."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:53.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What Scam felt was great pity for\NEri from the bottom of his heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:59.59,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's horrible for someone to live a\Nlife where happiness can never be..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.24,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the only thought\Nthat filled Scam's mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Eri... Eri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.30,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't want us to die together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted us to live together."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Scam's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was only gone for a short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle and I are both looking for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.29,RAINBOW31,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanen Apartments
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:07.91,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--You find him?\N--No, no luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.50,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't gone back home, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.52,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? I hope Scam\Nisn't thinking of doing anything bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.49,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.00,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the type to roll over and die that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.23,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:32.18,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about how tough\Nhe is more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.89,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have faith in Scam and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:36.98,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0420,,Yeah, Nomoto's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,"One month later"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:52.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'll be finished with his work soon,\Nso don't worry, he'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.82,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NThank you for always being so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:00.29,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm the one\Nwho talked him into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:18.92,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Scam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I took money that our family needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.38,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I worried Kazuo and Tatsuo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:37.72,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I even lied to Turtle and my friends\Nto borrow money from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:43.47,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used that money to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.87,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,To...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.98,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for us to have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:54.96,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I better get started on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you join us too, Maeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.79,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, s-sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.14,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:09.62,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.08,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.69,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.66,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It's only a little part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.61,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Soldier's by mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.58,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.46,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Working at a construction site in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.40,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to pay you guys\Nback as quickly as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.85,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you did manual labor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.73,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.\NI actually worked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.35,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:04.09,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Time to call all the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.10,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We're drinking all night tonight at Mario's bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.34,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're paying, of course!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.32,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna drink 'til we puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.78,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I don't have any money left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:25.28,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush!\NThere's a crapload of girls out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:29.80,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Even girls in junior high now will be\Ngrown women in five or six years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:33.02,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That's smart thinking, Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.67,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.15,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after it was burned in the war,\Nit still grows new buds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.95,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,It has amazing vitality...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:20:00.47,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I waited\Nhere like Eri told me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.99,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,But she committed suicide\Nwith another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:10.13,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything she told me was a fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:15.56,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind went completely blank after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:22.01,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,and before I realized it,\NI was standing here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:28.55,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I saw a small bud\Ncoming out of this tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.65,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.77,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I really heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:40.51,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri's voice, saying, "Live!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.71,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new bud coming out\Nof the burned gingko tree{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.57,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}gave Scam the encouragement to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.60,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That's right;\NI can't let this discourage me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:59.03,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Life is full of encounters and farewells."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:06.93,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scam vowed, "Eri. I will live."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.31,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Watch me too, Anchan and Dad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:17.44,RAINBOW30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will live on, steadfastly and wisely."{\i0}
